import classes from './BookRooms.module.css' import Title from '../UI/Title' function BookRooms() { return (
<div className={classes.bookingSection}> <label className={classes.bookingLabels} htmlFor='fromDate'>Check-in</label> <input className={classes.inputFields} type='date'></input> <label className={classes.bookingLabels} htmlFor='toDate'>Check-out</label> <input className={classes.inputFields} type='date'></input> </div> </div> ) } export default BookRooms
